fix single quote char (Slamdunk) > * feature [#3340](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3340) Verbose LintingException after fixing (Slamdunk) > * feature [#3423](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3423) FunctionToConstantFixer - add fix "get_called_class" option (SpacePossum) > * feature [#3434](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3434) Add PhpUnitSetUpTearDownVisibilityFixer (BackEndTea, SpacePossum) > * feature [#3442](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3442) Add CommentToPhpdocFixer (kubawerlos, keradus) > * feature [#3448](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3448) OrderedClassElementsFixer - added sortAlgorithm option (meridius) > * feature [#3454](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3454) Add StringLineEndingFixer (iluuu1994, SpacePossum, keradus, julienfalque) > * feature [#3477](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3477) PhpUnitStrictFixer: handle static calls (Slamdunk) > * feature [#3479](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3479) PhpUnitConstructFixer: handle static calls (Slamdunk) > * feature [#3507](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3507) Add PhpUnitOrderedCoversFixer (Slamdunk) > * feature [#3545](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3545) Add the 'none' sort algorithm to OrderedImportsFixer (EvgenyOrekhov) > * feature [#3588](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3588) Add NoAlternativeSyntaxFixer (eddmash, keradus) > * minor [#3414](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3414) DescribeCommand: add fixer class when verbose (Slamdunk) > * minor [#3432](https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/issues/3432) ConfigurationDefinitionFixerInterface -
